description: This common Gatinho purrs with a rating of 40, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 40, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 3 for East, Nine Lives for South, and 3 for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [40 Votes, Common]
